established as a new type of contemporary marxist party said a 
draft declaration reported by the official bta news agency 
the report did not say when the drafts were formulated or by 
whom usually such draft documents are done by senior party members 
the political system of democratic socialism implies a 
multiparty system parliamentary democracy separation of 
