palace in tokyo on nov 12 while the daijosai or great food 
offering ritual will be conducted according to customs of the 
shinto religion on the evening of nov 22 and will last into the 
following day 
akihito 56 assumed the chrysanthemum throne when his father 
hirohito died of cancer at age 87 on jan 7 1989 but he and 
