thornburgh overturned an immigration appeals board decision to 
reopen dohertys deportation case 
the hearing thursday stemmed from dohertys appeal of the 
rulings by meese and thornburgh if his appeal is successful 
doherty will be granted another round in immigration courts this 
time to apply for political asylum 
as throughout his legal battle emotions ran high at the 
hearing doherty was not present but the courtroom was filled with 
his supporters 
