improperly intervened in dohertys case 
what we see in this case is the naked manipulation of an 
administrative proceeding pike told the three judges hearing the 
appeal 
she said the central issue was that the attorney general is 
not above the law and that no individual including my client is 
outside the law 
pike also noted that 46 members of congress had signed a brief 
supporting dohertys position 
