providing for the destruction of tons of chemical weapons and he 
promised that soviet military maneuvers would be restructured to 
reduce environmental damage 
in the speech which ended the fiveday conference in moscow he 
called for international environmental monitoring and control that 
is another item of considerable use to the soviet union which has 
only recently begun to calculate its pollution levels the water in 
many cities is too fouled to drink and toxic waste dumps are often 
open pools of deadly chemicals 
gorbachev suggested the development of international standards 
to protect areas of particular concern for the entire world such 
as the antarctic he mentioned tropical forests coral reefs and 
lake baikal in the soviet union 
focusing on the soviet union he promised to triple the number 
of preserves of pristine wilderness in the next decade 
he also suggested that an environmental conference planned for 
brazil in 1992 be held at the highest level to approve a code 
of ecological ethics 
