<TEXT>
after rightists read in the newspaper that masaaki 
nakajima was active in a group working for the rights of 
foreigners they drove a militarystyle truck to his quiet 
neighborhood in suburban tokyo 
for two days nakajima says men in khaki uniforms harangued his 
