motoshima that began after the mayor said in december 1988 that 
hirohito then dying of cancer shares responsibility for the 
war as well as all of us who lived in that period 
a year earlier tajiri said in a tv interview that he was 
willing to kill for his beliefs because after all rightwingers 
are terrorists 
the rightists also have targeted conservative politicians and 
groups 
last year a rightist group reportedly sent a severed finger to 
