winstonsalem nc ap rj reynolds tobacco co announced 
friday it will cancel its philadelphia test marketing of a 
cigarette aimed at blacks saying the companys efforts have been 
misrepresented by smoking opponents 
the move came a day after the countrys top health official 
blasted reynolds slick and sinister cigarette ad campaign and 
said tobacco companies were putting profits above the health of the 
poor and minorities 
peter hoult rjr executive vice president of marketing said 
we regret that a small coalition of antismoking zealots 
apparently believes that black smokers are somehow different from 
others who choose to smoke and must not be allowed to exercise the 
same freedom of choice available to all other smokers 
this represents a loss of choice for black smokers and a 
further erosion of the freeenterprise system he said our 
sole purpose plainly and simply was to test market a cigarette 
among smokers who currently buy competitive products 
uptown a new menthol brand of cigarette had been scheduled for 
test marketing beginning feb 5 in philadelphia 
the company had said the ads would target blacks who as a 
group prefer menthol cigarettes rj reynolds also said 
philadelphia was chosen because its population is 40 percent black 
