services secretary louis sullivan accused rj reynolds of trying 
to create a culture of cancer with uptown 
we must resist the unworthy efforts of the tobacco merchants 
to earn profits at the expense of the health and wellbeing of our 
poor and minority citizens he said this tradeoff between 
profits and good health must stop 
