thencincinnati financier charles keating in 1974 or 1975 but he 
backed off that story when cincinnati bell lawyers showed that 
gabor was working in new york for american telephone amp telegraph 
co at that time 
wild rumors changed stories bumping into facts and refusal 
to take polygraph tests what does that say about their case 
morelli said 
