sellars 
as in his first batch of ideas moyers doesnt fear the term 
talking heads shots of interviewer and subject talking for 
some tv executives of the keepitmoving mtv generation talking 
heads mean many turnoffs 
sometimes they are turnoffs he concedes in his soft texas 
accent the question is are the talking heads thinking minds and 
thinking people are they interesting to watch i think the most 
fascinating production value is the human face 
moyers press secretary to president lyndon b johnson then 
publisher of newsday newspaper before finding tv a bully pulpit for 
