when dismayed he left that arena 
however like former cbs correspondent ike pappas he does worry 
that some of network news is dominated now by producers which 
is not itself a bad thing if they started out as reporters and 
journalists 
but if all they know is pictures and editing then the success 
of the piece is at the expense of the journalist 
still he says some network newscasts he has seen mostly on 
