government issues gained 332 point to point intermediate 
maturities rose 516 point to 716 point and longterm issues 
advanced 1932 point according to figures provided by telerate 
inc a financial information service 
the movement of a point is equivalent to a change of 10 in the 
price of a bond with a 1000 face value 
